2/13(월)

"Network addressing using the InetAddress class"
    Unicast : one address
    Multicast : more than one address

    InetAddress class : static get type methods
    URL(Uniform Recource Locator)

        InetAddress address = InetAddress.getByName("www.~~")


"NIO support" (New In Out)
    channel  : This represents a stream of data between applications
               1) File
               2) Datagram
               3) Socket

    Buffer   : This works with a channel to process data
               임시 저장공간
               ex) 놀이기구 대기줄 막아둔 철장(미리 담아뒀다가 열어서 보냄) 물탱크, 정화시설, 댐

    Selector : This is a technology that allows a single thread to handle multiple channels
               ex) 하나의 채널에 여러개 동작되도록


    TCP : 정해진 프로토콜 안에서~~?
    UDP : 같은 네트워크 안에서~~?


